* Input filename (string) * tp_info.dat
* Reference clock frequency (Hz) (float) * 10240000
* Input sampling interval (us) (float) * 100
* Dejittering filter parameter (float) * 0.0004
* Loop filter parameter (float) * 0.0001
* PLL loop gain (float) * 0.0001
* System latency (us) (float) * 500
* Output filename (string) * tp_info.out
